  <eainfo>
    <detailed>
      <enttyp>
        <enttypl>asdi.planning_cadastre.PLSS_FIRSTDIVISION_BLM</enttypl>
        <enttypd>The PLSS First Division is commonly the section. This is the first set of divisions for a PLSS Township.</enttypd>
      </enttyp>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>FRSTDIVTYP</attrlabl>
        <attrdef>This is the type of first division and is commonly the section but may be a lot, parcel, tract or other division.</attrdef>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>FRSTDIVNO</attrlabl>
        <attrdef>This is the number, letter or designator for the first division of the PLSS Township</attrdef>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>FRSTDIVTXT</attrlabl>
        <attrdef>This is the first division type as a text field</attrdef>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>FRSTDIVID</attrlabl>
        <attrdef>This is a unique identifier for the first division that is built by appending the first division elements on the Township identifier.</attrdef>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>OBJECTID</attrlabl>
        <attrdef>Internal feature number.</attrdef>
        <attrdefs>ESRI</attrdefs>
        <attrdomv>
          <udom>Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.</udom>
        </attrdomv>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>st_area(shape)</attrlabl>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>st_length(shape)</attrlabl>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>FRSTDIVLAB</attrlabl>
        <attrdef>This is the label for the first division that is used for cartographic of web display purposes</attrdef>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>globalid</attrlabl>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>PLSSID</attrlabl>
        <attrdef>This is the unique identifier for the PLSS Township in which the first division is located. Concatenation of the principal meridian, township, range, and duplication code that form a unique identifier for the township.</attrdef>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>FRSTDIVDUP</attrlabl>
        <attrdef>This is a code to indicate whether the first division is a duplicated area or identifier</attrdef>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>SURVTYPTXT</attrlabl>
        <attrdef>The description of the survey type code. There may be a description of the survey type, or survey status in the case of this feature, without a code.</attrdef>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>SHAPE</attrlabl>
        <attrdef>Feature geometry.</attrdef>
        <attrdefs>ESRI</attrdefs>
        <attrdomv>
          <udom>Coordinates defining the features.</udom>
        </attrdomv>
      </attr>
      <attr>
        <attrlabl>SURVTYP</attrlabl>
        <attrdef>Code for the type of special survey typically from the codes for the BLM data collection. Used in this feature to indicate if the feature is unsurveyed or unprotracted.</attrdef>
